dct_description_sm: Map shows relevant buildings, walls, wells, and temples. Includes table of reliability of data. "18 July 1945." "From: Sketch map of Cho-hsien, Chinese Local Histories, 1936 edition." "Lithographed in the Reproduction Branch, OSS." "No. 7291--R & A, OSS." Includes location inset.
